A '''Luxum''' [[Crystal/Legends|crystal]] was a type of [[Lightsaber crystal/Legends|crystal]] that could be used in [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] construction. These crystals were from the world of [[Ambria/Legends|Ambria]], a planet gripped by dark energies, where they were formed out of the minerals and [[The Force/Legends|Force]] energy contained in [[Lake Natth]] through long and deep meditation.<ref name="TCSWE">{{CSWECite|II|268|Luxum crystal}}</ref> They were more effective against [[Droid/Legends|droids]], imparting an ion effect to a lightsaber blade when used the construction of the weapon.<ref name="KotOR">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref> Luxum crystals were one type of mineral sought out by fugitive [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Jax Pavan]] in his search for a mineral with which to construct a new lightsaber after losing his in a fight with [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]].<ref name="Street of Shadows">''[[Coruscant Nights II: Street of Shadows]]''</ref>

